Pleasant atmosphere
Vesna Konhäuser has been attending the Rakoczi Festival in Bad Kissingen with her husband for over 25 years.
She did so in this Covid year, too.
The couple settled down at the Luitpold Casino, watched the historic characters promenade, and listened to live Cuban music from the casino’s restaurant.
“I’m think it’s still really pleasant like this,” said Konhäuser.
She wasn’t missing the crowds of people which are usually associated with the Rakoczi.
