There will surely be more to come.
We are also not naive and have a lot of patience.”
Employees or trade unions concerned often reported the abuse.
In addition, the BA uses analysis software to identify patterns of abuse.
According to Terzenbach, the BA is preparing for a possible wave of bankruptcy in the fall.
“Will there be significantly more bankruptcies than in the previous year?
